This package bundles tokenizer assets derived from official Hugging Face repositories under the AIDC-AI organization:
- AIDC-AI/Marco-o1 tokenizer.json

This package also registers the following official AIDC-AI models after verifying
that their tokenizer.json files are identical to already-supported qwen families:
- AIDC-AI/Marco-Nano-Instruct
- AIDC-AI/Marco-Mini-Global-Base
- AIDC-AI/Marco-Mini-Base
- AIDC-AI/Marco-Nano-Base
- AIDC-AI/Marco-LLM-SEA
- AIDC-AI/Marco-LLM-AR-V4
- AIDC-AI/Marco-LLM-AR-V2
- AIDC-AI/Marco-LLM-ES

